<!DOCTYPE html>
html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    title Simon W. Bloom / Work
    include ./includes/head.pug
  body(id="work")
    header.hero-container.hero-container--internal.hero-container--work
      .hero.wrapper
        .hero-nav-wrapper
          .hero-content-wrapper
            .logo
              a(href="/")
                img(src='/public/images/svgs/swb-badge-blog.svg' alt='a small paper crane').logo-desktop
                img(src='/public/images/svgs/swb-mobile-logo.svg' alt='a small paper crane').logo-mobile
            nav
              include ./includes/nav.pug
        .hero-text-wrapper
          span.hero-subtext A collection of projects & contracts
          h1 Work
          span.hero-subtext From large agencies to nonprofits
    main
      .wrapper
        .intro-box
          .intro-box-body I love #[strong long-term contracts]. They allow me to #[strong integrate] with talented teams, meet new people, and collaborate to create amazing digital experiences. I'm flexible, friendly, and love a good #[strong challenge].
          .intro-box-featured.intro-box-featured--suitcase
            img(src="./images/pngs/work-briefcase.png" alt='a briefcase')
    .portfolio-short-outercontainer
      .portfolio-short-container
          .wrapper
            .portfolio-short
              .portfolio-short-body
                span.portfolio-category Lead Instructor
                h2 HackerYou
                strong Snatch the pebble from my hand, grasshopper.
                p Taking twenty-six students from fledgling students to battle-ready junior developers ready to take on their first professional roles in Toronto's tech vibrant community and beyond.
                a(class="btn-outer hvr-rectangle-in" href="/case-studies/hackeryou/")
                  .btn-inner Read On
                picture.portfolio-short-mobile-image
                  source(srcset="/images/pngs/work-item1-geometry-2x.png" media="(min-device-pixel-ratio: 2), (min-resolution: 192dpi)")
                  img(src="/images/pngs/work-item1-geometry.png" width="264px" alt='a geometric shape')
              .portfolio-short-feature
    .portfolio-short-outercontainer
      .portfolio-short-container
          .wrapper
            .portfolio-short
              .portfolio-short-feature
              .portfolio-short-body
                span.portfolio-category Agency Contract
                h2 Jam3
                strong Make cool shit- and don't fuck it up.
                p Jam3 is one of the world's top digital and production design agencies. They specialize in creating highly advanced, experiential works in both the advertising and entertainment industry.
                a(class="btn-outer hvr-rectangle-in" href="#")
                  .btn-inner Read On
                picture.portfolio-short-mobile-image
                  source(srcset="/images/pngs/work-item2-geometry-2x.png" media="(min-device-pixel-ratio: 2), (min-resolution: 192dpi)")
                  img(src="/images/pngs/work-item2-geometry.png" width="264px" alt='a geometric shape')
    .portfolio-short-outercontainer
      .portfolio-short-container
          .wrapper
            .portfolio-short
              .portfolio-short-body
                span.portfolio-category A Digital Pilgrimage
                h2 3 Months, 8 Countries
                strong Travelling through South East Asia as a Digital Nomad
                p In 2016, I took a three month sabbatical to deepen my skills as a Front End Developer. So why not do it while exploring the world?
                a(class="btn-outer hvr-rectangle-in" href="/case-studies/digital-nomad/")
                  .btn-inner Read On
                picture.portfolio-short-mobile-image
                  source(srcset="/images/pngs/work-item3-geometry-2x.png" media="(min-device-pixel-ratio: 2), (min-resolution: 192dpi)")
                  img(src="/images/pngs/work-item3-geometry.png" width="264px" alt='a geometric shape')
              .portfolio-short-feature
    include ./includes/footer.pug
